              'biography': 'Georgy Kucherin is a junior researcher at Kaspersky\u2019s Global Research and Analysis Team and a fourth-year student at Moscow State University. He is passionate about analysis of complex malware and reverse engineering. His previous research includes attribution of the SolarWinds attack, as well as thorough investigations into APTs such as Operation Triangulation, Turla, FinFisher, APT41 and Lazarus.',
