              'biography': 'Author, researcher, journalist at netzpolitik.org. I am a journalist and communication scientist. I have been an editor at netzpolitik.org since 2016, where I co-host the Off/On podcast. I am interested in questions of power in digitalisation. My topics are surveillance capitalism, digital civil society and the digital public sphere. To be more specific: I often write about data misuse and data protection, online advertising, digital election campaigns, platform regulation, transparency, lobbying and right-wing extremism in the police.',
