              'biography': 'IT Security researcher at Fraunhofer SIT in Muenster. Formerly PhD student at Muenster University of Applied Sciences and 10 years in embedded/automotive IT Security.\r\n\r\nResearch interest: IT Security in medical systems and the Telematikinfrastruktur (TI).',
