              'biography': 'Board member of CCC e.V. derf has been active at CCC D\u00fcsseldorf / Chaosdorf since 2007 and is a board member of Chaosdorf e.V. since 2016. In addition to the usual bureaucracy business, this also gave her insights into handling conflicts *without* being able to rely on structures such as awareness team or arbitration board. She joined the board of CCC e.V. in 2021.',
