              'biography': 'Maja G\u00f6pel is a political economist and expert in sustainability policy and transformation research. She holds a professorship at the Leuphana University of L\u00fcneburg.',
              'links': [{ 'url': 'https://www.maja-goepel.de', 'title': 'maja-goepel.de' }]
