              'avatar_url': 'https://fahrplan.events.ccc.de/congress/2023/fahrplan/system/people/avatars/000/019/384/large/Kim.jpg?1703662166',
              'biography': '- Climate Justice activist and active in resistance for a sustainable world\r\n- Computer Science Student and interested in digital rights\r\n- Since 2021 active in the struggle against colonialism in S\u00e1pmi\r\n- Helped organising the Decolonise-S\u00e1pmi Infotour in 2023',
