            'track': null,
            'type': 'other',
            'abstract': '',
            'description': 'This will be a great opportunity for members of the community to meet each other and socialise, as well as an opportunity for anyone interested in Tor to come and meet each other and become part of the Tor community.\r\n\r\nThere will be a talk by Q Misell on progress with ACME for Onion Services.\r\n\r\nLocation: TBC',
