            'description': 'Let\'s chat some LLM agents, their uses, and their governance. We can start by going over how to create one. We can then chat:\r\n - How do I create LLM agents in ChatGPT? What can we use them for?\r\n - How does this differ from finetuning?\r\n - How does this look with open-source models?\r\n - What business models might Big Tech come up with for LLM agents?\r\n - What are good ways for civil society to hold LLM agent producers accountable?\r\n - ...',
