            'language': 'de, en',
            'track': null,
            'type': 'other',
            'abstract': '',
            'description': 'I think the Advent of Code (https://www.adventofcode.com) is a great Advent calendar. But some of the puzzles are rather more difficult, and I don\'t have time to do them every day, so there are still a few puzzles left unsolved. I think many of you feel the same way.\r\n\r\nThis is an invitation to meet and crack the last puzzles together. It\'s always more fun together.\r\n\r\nI have solved my puzzles in Kotlin and can also provide support for Java, Python, Dart and JavaScript.',
