            'track': null,
            'type': 'other',
            'abstract': '',
            'description': '**attention: Meeting will be on Dec. 30, 0:00; the webpage is confusing in this case**\r\n\r\ntorservers.net is a global network of non-profits running Tor relays.\r\nIt has been inactive for quite some time.\r\nThis meeting is for all non-profits who are running Tor relays.\r\nThe goal is to discuss and maybe build a future for torservers.net.',
