            'room': 'Kidspace - Workshopraum in Saal B',
            'slug': '37c3-937706-lightning-talks-kids-edition',
            'url': 'https://events.ccc.de/congress/2023/hub/event/lightning-talks-kids-edition/',
            'title': 'Lightning Talks - Kids Edition',
            'subtitle': null,
            'language': null,
            'track': null,
            'type': 'other',
            'abstract': 'Liebe Kinder, das ist eure Zeit zu gl\u00e4nzen! Am 3. Congress-Tag \u00f6ffnen wir im Workshopraum des Kidspace eine B\u00fchne nur f\u00fcr euch. Teilt eure spannenden Projekte, genialen Erfindungen oder kreativen Geschichten in unseren Kinder-Lightning Talks.',
            'description': 'Dear children, this is your time to shine! On the 3rd Congress day, we will open a stage just for you in the Kidspace workshop room. Share your exciting projects, ingenious inventions or creative stories in our Kids\u2019 Lightning Talks. \ud83d\ude80\r\n\r\n\ud83c\udf08 Bring your models, drawings or just your amazing thoughts. Whether it\u2019s a self-built robot car, a fantastic drawing story or a clever app idea - we want to see what inspires you!\r\n\r\n\ud83d\udc49 Registration: Come to Kidspace and register with the organizers. Show what you can do in a short talk and share your passion with other young explorers!',
