              'id': 4819,
              'name': 'Helga Velroyen',
              'avatar_url': null,
              'biography': 'Geek and nerd, hard of hearing, disability inclusion advocate, CCC member, amateur artist, part-time goth, crazy old cat lady, she/her. Founder of "Doofe Ohren", a project to explain hearing aid technology for everyone. http://www.doofe-ohren.de',
              'links': []
