              'biography': 'Janna has a background in Environmental Chemistry and Health from Copenhagen University and works for BUND eV as a chemicals and consumer protection senior policy officer. She was a founding member of the open laboratory Curious Community Labs eV in Hamburg and the agroforestry project Feld Food Forest eV in Berlin and is a part-time vegetable farmer.',
